  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of EMINENT study is to evaluate the efficacy of Xuezhikang or atorvastatin in
      hypertensive patients at low/moderate cardiovascular risk.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      EMINENT study is to evaluate the efficacy of Xuezhikang or atorvastatin on vascular function
      protection in hypertensive patients at low/moderate cardiovascular risk.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
